{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":1000,"text":"A public, Dewey long ago observed,"},{"time":4000,"text":"is constituted through discussion and debate."},{"time":8000,"text":"If we are to call the tyranny of assumptions into question,"},{"time":14000,"text":"and avoid doxa, the realm of the unquestioned,"},{"time":18000,"text":"then we must be willing to subject our own assumptions"},{"time":21000,"text":"to debate and discussion."},{"time":25000,"text":"It is in this spirit that I join into a discussion"},{"time":30000,"text":"of one of the critical issues of our time,"},{"time":33000,"text":"namely, how to mobilize different forms of capital"},{"time":37000,"text":"for the project of state building."}]},{"cues":[{"time":39000,"text":"To put the assumptions very clearly:"},{"time":42000,"text":"capitalism, after 150 years, has become acceptable,"},{"time":47000,"text":"and so has democracy."},{"time":49000,"text":"If we looked in the world of 1945"},{"time":53000,"text":"and looked at the map of capitalist economies and democratic polities,"},{"time":58000,"text":"they were the rare exception, not the norm."},{"time":63000,"text":"The question now, however,"},{"time":65000,"text":"is both about which form of capitalism"},{"time":70000,"text":"and which type of democratic participation."},{"time":74000,"text":"But we must acknowledge"},{"time":76000,"text":"that this moment has brought about"},{"time":78000,"text":"a rare consensus of assumptions."},{"time":81000,"text":"And that provides the ground"},{"time":84000,"text":"for a type of action,"},{"time":86000,"text":"because consensus of each moment"},{"time":88000,"text":"allows us to act."},{"time":90000,"text":"And it is necessary, no matter how fragile"},{"time":93000,"text":"or how provisional our consensus,"},{"time":96000,"text":"to be able to move forward."}]},{"cues":[{"time":98000,"text":"But the majority of the world"},{"time":101000,"text":"neither benefits from capitalism"},{"time":103000,"text":"nor from democratic systems."},{"time":109000,"text":"Most of the globe"},{"time":111000,"text":"experiences the state as repressive,"},{"time":115000,"text":"as an organization that is concerned"},{"time":118000,"text":"about denial of rights,"},{"time":120000,"text":"about denial of justice,"},{"time":122000,"text":"rather than provision of it."},{"time":126000,"text":"And in terms of experience of capitalism,"},{"time":129000,"text":"there are two aspects"},{"time":131000,"text":"that the rest of the globe experiences."},{"time":133000,"text":"First, extractive industry."},{"time":135000,"text":"Blood diamonds, smuggled emeralds,"},{"time":138000,"text":"timber,"},{"time":141000,"text":"that is cut right from under the poorest."},{"time":144000,"text":"Second is technical assistance."},{"time":147000,"text":"And technical assistance might shock you,"},{"time":149000,"text":"but it's the worst form"},{"time":151000,"text":"of -- today -- of the ugly face"},{"time":154000,"text":"of the developed world to the developing countries."},{"time":158000,"text":"Tens of billions of dollars"},{"time":160000,"text":"are supposedly spent on building capacity"},{"time":162000,"text":"with people who are paid up to 1,500 dollars a day,"},{"time":166000,"text":"who are incapable"},{"time":168000,"text":"of thinking creatively,"},{"time":170000,"text":"or organically."}]},{"cues":[{"time":176000,"text":"Next assumption --"},{"time":178000,"text":"and of course the events of July 7,"},{"time":180000,"text":"I express my deep sympathy, and before that, September 11 --"},{"time":183000,"text":"have reminded us"},{"time":185000,"text":"we do not live in three different worlds."},{"time":188000,"text":"We live in one world."},{"time":192000,"text":"But that's easily said."},{"time":195000,"text":"But we are not dealing with the implications"},{"time":198000,"text":"of the one world that we are living in."},{"time":202000,"text":"And that is that if we want to have one world,"},{"time":205000,"text":"this one world cannot be based"},{"time":207000,"text":"on huge pockets of exclusion,"},{"time":210000,"text":"and then inclusion for some."},{"time":212000,"text":"We must now finally come"},{"time":214000,"text":"to think about the premises"},{"time":216000,"text":"of a truly global world,"},{"time":218000,"text":"in relationship to the regime of rights"},{"time":220000,"text":"and responsibilities and accountabilities"},{"time":223000,"text":"that are truly global in scope."},{"time":225000,"text":"Otherwise we will be missing"},{"time":228000,"text":"this open moment in history,"},{"time":230000,"text":"where we have a consensus"},{"time":232000,"text":"on both the form of politics"},{"time":234000,"text":"and the form of economics."}]},{"cues":[{"time":237000,"text":"What is one of these organizations to pick?"},{"time":239000,"text":"We have three critical terms:"},{"time":241000,"text":"economy,"},{"time":243000,"text":"civil society"},{"time":245000,"text":"and the state."},{"time":247000,"text":"I will not deal with those first two, except to say"},{"time":250000,"text":"that uncritical transfer of assumptions,"},{"time":253000,"text":"from one context to another,"},{"time":255000,"text":"can only make for disaster."},{"time":258000,"text":"Economics"},{"time":261000,"text":"taught in most of the elite universities"},{"time":264000,"text":"are practically useless in my context."},{"time":267000,"text":"My country is dominated"},{"time":269000,"text":"by drug economy and a mafia."},{"time":272000,"text":"Textbook economics does not work in my context,"},{"time":274000,"text":"and I have very few recommendations from anybody"},{"time":277000,"text":"as to how to put together a legal economy."},{"time":280000,"text":"The poverty of our knowledge"},{"time":282000,"text":"must become the first basis"},{"time":284000,"text":"of moving forward,"},{"time":286000,"text":"and not imposition of the framework"},{"time":289000,"text":"that works on the basis of mathematical modeling,"},{"time":292000,"text":"for which I have enormous respect."},{"time":294000,"text":"My colleagues at Johns Hopkins were among the best."}]},{"cues":[{"time":298000,"text":"Second,"},{"time":300000,"text":"instead of debating endlessly"},{"time":303000,"text":"about what is the structure of the state,"},{"time":305000,"text":"why don't we simplify"},{"time":307000,"text":"and say, what are a series of functions"},{"time":309000,"text":"that the state in the 21st century must perform?"},{"time":312000,"text":"Clare Lockhart and I are writing a book on this;"},{"time":315000,"text":"we hope to share that much widely with --"},{"time":317000,"text":"and third is that we could actually construct an index"},{"time":320000,"text":"to measure comparatively"},{"time":323000,"text":"how well these functions that we would agree on"},{"time":326000,"text":"are being performed in different places."}]},{"cues":[{"time":328000,"text":"So what are these functions?"},{"time":330000,"text":"We propose 10."},{"time":332000,"text":"And it's legitimate monopoly of means of violence,"},{"time":335000,"text":"administrative control, management of public finances,"},{"time":338000,"text":"investment in human capital, provision of citizenship rights,"},{"time":341000,"text":"provision of infrastructure,"},{"time":343000,"text":"management of the tangible and intangible assets of the state"},{"time":346000,"text":"through regulation, creation of the market,"},{"time":348000,"text":"international agreements, including public borrowing,"},{"time":351000,"text":"and then, most importantly, rule of law."}]},{"cues":[{"time":354000,"text":"I won't elaborate."},{"time":356000,"text":"I hope the questions will give me an opportunity."},{"time":359000,"text":"This is a feasible goal,"},{"time":361000,"text":"basically because, contrary to widespread assumption,"},{"time":364000,"text":"I would argue that we know how to do this."},{"time":367000,"text":"Who would have imagined that Germany"},{"time":369000,"text":"would be either united or democratic today,"},{"time":372000,"text":"if you looked at it from the perspective of Oxford of 1943?"},{"time":377000,"text":"But people at Oxford prepared for a democratic Germany"},{"time":380000,"text":"and engaged in planning."},{"time":383000,"text":"And there are lots of other examples."}]},{"cues":[{"time":387000,"text":"Now in order to do this -- and this brings this group --"},{"time":391000,"text":"we have to rethink the notion of capital."},{"time":394000,"text":"The least important form of capital, in this project,"},{"time":398000,"text":"is financial capital -- money."},{"time":402000,"text":"Money is not capital in most of the developing countries."},{"time":405000,"text":"It's just cash."},{"time":407000,"text":"Because it lacks the institutional,"},{"time":409000,"text":"organizational, managerial forms"},{"time":412000,"text":"to turn it into capital."},{"time":415000,"text":"And what is required"},{"time":418000,"text":"is a combination of physical capital,"},{"time":420000,"text":"institutional capital, human capital --"},{"time":422000,"text":"and security, of course, is critical,"},{"time":425000,"text":"but so is information."}]},{"cues":[{"time":427000,"text":"Now, the issue that should concern us here --"},{"time":430000,"text":"and that's the challenge"},{"time":432000,"text":"that I would like to pose to this group --"},{"time":436000,"text":"is again, it takes 16 years"},{"time":439000,"text":"in your countries"},{"time":442000,"text":"to produce somebody with a B.S. degree."},{"time":445000,"text":"It takes 20 years"},{"time":447000,"text":"to produce somebody with a Ph.D."},{"time":449000,"text":"The first challenge is to rethink,"},{"time":452000,"text":"fundamentally,"},{"time":455000,"text":"the issue of the time."},{"time":458000,"text":"Do we need to repeat"},{"time":462000,"text":"the modalities that we have inherited?"},{"time":464000,"text":"Our educational systems are inherited from the 19th century."},{"time":470000,"text":"What is it that we need to do fundamentally"},{"time":473000,"text":"to re-engage in a project,"},{"time":475000,"text":"that capital formation is rapid?"},{"time":478000,"text":"The absolute majority of the world's population"},{"time":481000,"text":"are below 20,"},{"time":483000,"text":"and they are growing larger and faster."},{"time":487000,"text":"They need different ways"},{"time":489000,"text":"of being approached,"},{"time":491000,"text":"different ways of being enfranchised,"},{"time":494000,"text":"different ways of being skilled."},{"time":496000,"text":"And that's the first thing."}]},{"cues":[{"time":498000,"text":"Second is, you're problem solvers,"},{"time":501000,"text":"but you're not engaging your global responsibility."},{"time":506000,"text":"You've stayed away"},{"time":508000,"text":"from the problems of corruption."},{"time":510000,"text":"You only want clean environments in which to function."},{"time":513000,"text":"But if you don't think through the problems of corruption,"},{"time":516000,"text":"who will?"},{"time":519000,"text":"You stay away from design for development."},{"time":522000,"text":"You're great designers,"},{"time":525000,"text":"but your designs are selfish."},{"time":528000,"text":"It's for your own immediate use."},{"time":531000,"text":"The world in which I operate"},{"time":534000,"text":"operates with designs"},{"time":536000,"text":"regarding roads, or dams,"},{"time":538000,"text":"or provision of electricity"},{"time":540000,"text":"that have not been revisited in 60 years."},{"time":544000,"text":"This is not right. It requires thinking."}]},{"cues":[{"time":547000,"text":"But, particularly, what we need"},{"time":549000,"text":"more than anything else from this group"},{"time":551000,"text":"is your imagination"},{"time":553000,"text":"to be brought to bear on problems"},{"time":555000,"text":"the way a meme is supposed to work."},{"time":559000,"text":"As the work on paradigms, long time ago showed --"},{"time":562000,"text":"Thomas Kuhn's work --"},{"time":564000,"text":"it's in the intersection of ideas"},{"time":566000,"text":"that new developments --"},{"time":568000,"text":"true breakthroughs -- occur."},{"time":570000,"text":"And I hope that this group"},{"time":572000,"text":"would be able to deal with the issue of state and development"},{"time":575000,"text":"and the empowerment of the majority of the world's poor,"},{"time":577000,"text":"through this means."},{"time":579000,"text":"Thank you."},{"time":581000,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":590000,"text":"Chris Anderson: So, Ashraf, until recently,"},{"time":593000,"text":"you were the finance minister of Afghanistan,"},{"time":595000,"text":"a country right at the middle"},{"time":597000,"text":"of much of the world's agenda."},{"time":599000,"text":"Is the country gonna make it?"},{"time":601000,"text":"Will democracy flourish? What scares you most?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":605000,"text":"Ashraf Ghani: What scares me most is -- is you,"},{"time":608000,"text":"lack of your engagement."},{"time":611000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":615000,"text":"You asked me. You know I always give the unconventional answer."},{"time":618000,"text":"No. But seriously,"},{"time":620000,"text":"the issue of Afghanistan"},{"time":622000,"text":"first has to be seen as,"},{"time":624000,"text":"at least, a 10- to 20-year perspective."},{"time":628000,"text":"Today the world of globalization"},{"time":630000,"text":"is on speed."},{"time":632000,"text":"Time has been compressed."},{"time":634000,"text":"And space does not exist for most people."},{"time":637000,"text":"But in my world --"},{"time":639000,"text":"you know, when I went back to Afghanistan after 23 years,"},{"time":642000,"text":"space had expanded."},{"time":644000,"text":"Every conceivable form of infrastructure had broken down."},{"time":647000,"text":"I rode -- traveled --"},{"time":649000,"text":"travel between two cities that used to take three hours"},{"time":652000,"text":"now took 12."},{"time":654000,"text":"So the first is when the scale is that,"},{"time":657000,"text":"we need to recognize"},{"time":659000,"text":"that just the simple things that are infrastructure --"},{"time":662000,"text":"it takes six years to deliver infrastructure."},{"time":664000,"text":"In our world."},{"time":666000,"text":"Any meaningful sort of thing."},{"time":669000,"text":"But the modality of attention,"},{"time":672000,"text":"or what is happening today, what's happening tomorrow."}]},{"cues":[{"time":675000,"text":"Second is,"},{"time":677000,"text":"when a country has been subjected"},{"time":680000,"text":"to one of the most immense, brutal forms of exercise of power --"},{"time":683000,"text":"we had the Red Army"},{"time":685000,"text":"for 10 continuous years,"},{"time":687000,"text":"110,000 strong,"},{"time":690000,"text":"literally terrorizing."},{"time":693000,"text":"The sky:"},{"time":695000,"text":"every Afghan"},{"time":698000,"text":"sees the sky as a source of fear."},{"time":702000,"text":"We were bombed"},{"time":704000,"text":"practically out of existence."},{"time":709000,"text":"Then, tens of thousands of people were trained in terrorism --"},{"time":714000,"text":"from all sides."},{"time":716000,"text":"The United States, Great Britain, joined for instance,"},{"time":718000,"text":"Egyptian intelligence service"},{"time":720000,"text":"to train thousands of people"},{"time":722000,"text":"in resistance and urban terrorism."},{"time":726000,"text":"How to turn a bicycle"},{"time":728000,"text":"into an instrument of terror."},{"time":731000,"text":"How to turn a donkey, a carthorse, anything."},{"time":734000,"text":"And the Russians, equally."},{"time":736000,"text":"So, when violence erupts"},{"time":738000,"text":"in a country like Afghanistan,"},{"time":740000,"text":"it's because of that legacy."},{"time":742000,"text":"But we have to understand"},{"time":744000,"text":"that we've been incredibly lucky."},{"time":746000,"text":"I mean, I really can't believe how lucky I am here,"},{"time":749000,"text":"standing in front of you, speaking."},{"time":752000,"text":"When I joined as finance minister,"},{"time":756000,"text":"I thought that the chances of my living more than three years"},{"time":759000,"text":"would not be more than five percent."},{"time":763000,"text":"Those were the risks. They were worth it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":766000,"text":"I think we can make it,"},{"time":768000,"text":"and the reason we can make it"},{"time":770000,"text":"is because of the people."},{"time":772000,"text":"You see, because, I mean -- I give you one statistic."},{"time":775000,"text":"91 percent of the men in Afghanistan,"},{"time":777000,"text":"86 percent of the women,"},{"time":779000,"text":"listen to at least three radio stations a day."},{"time":783000,"text":"In terms of their discourse,"},{"time":786000,"text":"in terms of their sophistication of knowledge of the world,"},{"time":789000,"text":"I think that I would dare say,"},{"time":792000,"text":"they're much more sophisticated"},{"time":794000,"text":"than rural Americans with college degrees"},{"time":799000,"text":"and the bulk of Europeans --"},{"time":803000,"text":"because the world matters to them."},{"time":806000,"text":"And what is their predominant concern?"},{"time":808000,"text":"Abandonment."},{"time":810000,"text":"Afghans have become deeply internationalist."}]},{"cues":[{"time":814000,"text":"You know, when I went back in December of 2001,"},{"time":816000,"text":"I had absolutely no desire to work with the Afghan government"},{"time":819000,"text":"because I'd lived as a nationalist."},{"time":821000,"text":"And I told them -- my people, with the Americans here --"},{"time":824000,"text":"separate."},{"time":826000,"text":"Yes, I have an advisory position with the U.N."},{"time":829000,"text":"I went through 10 Afghan provinces very rapidly."},{"time":831000,"text":"And everybody was telling me it was a different world."},{"time":834000,"text":"You know, they engage."},{"time":836000,"text":"They see engagement, global engagement,"},{"time":839000,"text":"as absolutely necessary to the future of the ordinary people."},{"time":842000,"text":"And the thing that the ordinary Afghan is most concerned with is --"},{"time":845000,"text":"Clare Lockhart is here,"},{"time":847000,"text":"so I'll recite a discussion she had"},{"time":849000,"text":"with an illiterate woman in Northern Afghanistan."},{"time":852000,"text":"And that woman said she didn't care"},{"time":854000,"text":"whether she had food on her table."},{"time":856000,"text":"What she worried about was whether there was a plan for the future,"},{"time":859000,"text":"where her children could really have a different life."},{"time":862000,"text":"That gives me hope."},{"time":866000,"text":"CA: How is Afghanistan"},{"time":868000,"text":"going to provide alternative income"},{"time":870000,"text":"to the many people"},{"time":872000,"text":"who are making their living off the drugs trade?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":874000,"text":"AG: Certainly. Well, the first is,"},{"time":876000,"text":"instead of sending a billion dollars"},{"time":879000,"text":"on drug eradication"},{"time":881000,"text":"and paying it to a couple of security companies,"},{"time":884000,"text":"they should give this hundred billion dollars"},{"time":886000,"text":"to 50"},{"time":889000,"text":"of the most critically innovative companies in the world"},{"time":893000,"text":"to ask them to create one million jobs."},{"time":896000,"text":"The key to the drug eradication is jobs."},{"time":898000,"text":"Look, there's a very little known fact:"},{"time":900000,"text":"countries that have a legal average income per capita of 1,000 dollars"},{"time":903000,"text":"don't produce drugs."}]},{"cues":[{"time":907000,"text":"Second, textile."},{"time":910000,"text":"Trade is the key, not aid."},{"time":913000,"text":"The U.S. and Europe"},{"time":915000,"text":"should give us a zero percent tariff."},{"time":917000,"text":"The textile industry is incredibly mobile."},{"time":920000,"text":"If you want us to be able to compete with China and to attract investment,"},{"time":923000,"text":"we could probably attract"},{"time":925000,"text":"four to six billion dollars"},{"time":927000,"text":"quite easily in the textile sector,"},{"time":929000,"text":"if there was zero tariffs --"},{"time":931000,"text":"would create the type of job."},{"time":934000,"text":"Cotton does not compete with opium;"},{"time":937000,"text":"a t-shirt does."},{"time":940000,"text":"And we need to understand, it's the value chain."},{"time":943000,"text":"Look, the ordinary Afghan is sick and tired"},{"time":946000,"text":"of hearing about microcredit."},{"time":949000,"text":"It is important,"},{"time":951000,"text":"but what the ordinary women and men who engage in micro-production want"},{"time":954000,"text":"is global access."},{"time":957000,"text":"They don't want to sell to the charity bazaars"},{"time":961000,"text":"that are only for foreigners --"},{"time":963000,"text":"and the same bloody shirt"},{"time":966000,"text":"embroidered time and again."},{"time":968000,"text":"What we want is a partnership"},{"time":970000,"text":"with the Italian design firms."},{"time":974000,"text":"Yeah, we have the best embroiderers in the world!"},{"time":978000,"text":"Why can't we do what was done with northern Italy?"},{"time":980000,"text":"With the Put Out system?"},{"time":984000,"text":"So I think economically,"},{"time":986000,"text":"the critical issue really is to now think through."}]},{"cues":[{"time":989000,"text":"And what I will say here is that aid doesn't work."},{"time":992000,"text":"You know, the aid system is broken."},{"time":995000,"text":"The aid system does not have the knowledge,"},{"time":997000,"text":"the vision, the ability."},{"time":999000,"text":"I'm all for it; after all, I raised a lot of it."},{"time":1002000,"text":"Yeah, to be exact, you know,"},{"time":1004000,"text":"I managed to persuade the world that"},{"time":1006000,"text":"they had to give my country 27.5 billion."},{"time":1008000,"text":"They didn't want to give us the money."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1010000,"text":"CA: And it still didn't work?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1012000,"text":"AG: No. It's not that it didn't work."},{"time":1014000,"text":"It's that a dollar of private investment,"},{"time":1016000,"text":"in my judgment,"},{"time":1018000,"text":"is equal at least to 20 dollars of aid,"},{"time":1021000,"text":"in terms of the dynamic that it generates."},{"time":1024000,"text":"Second is that one dollar of aid could be 10 cents;"},{"time":1027000,"text":"it could be 20 cents;"},{"time":1029000,"text":"or it could be four dollars."},{"time":1031000,"text":"It depends on what form it comes,"},{"time":1033000,"text":"what degrees of conditionalities are attached to it."},{"time":1036000,"text":"You know, the aid system, at first, was designed to benefit"},{"time":1039000,"text":"entrepreneurs of the developed countries,"},{"time":1041000,"text":"not to generate growth in the poor countries."},{"time":1046000,"text":"And this is, again, one of those assumptions --"},{"time":1048000,"text":"the way car seats are an assumption"},{"time":1051000,"text":"that we've inherited in governments, and doors."},{"time":1054000,"text":"You would think that the US government"},{"time":1056000,"text":"would not think that American firms needed subsidizing"},{"time":1059000,"text":"to function in developing countries, provide advice,"},{"time":1062000,"text":"but they do."},{"time":1064000,"text":"There's an entire weight of history"},{"time":1066000,"text":"vis-a-vis aid"},{"time":1068000,"text":"that now needs to be reexamined."},{"time":1070000,"text":"If the goal is to build states"},{"time":1073000,"text":"that can credibly take care of themselves --"},{"time":1076000,"text":"and I'm putting that proposition equally;"},{"time":1079000,"text":"you know I'm very harsh on my counterparts --"},{"time":1082000,"text":"aid must end"},{"time":1085000,"text":"in each country in a definable period."},{"time":1088000,"text":"And every year there must be progress"},{"time":1091000,"text":"on mobilization of domestic revenue"},{"time":1094000,"text":"and generation of the economy."},{"time":1097000,"text":"Unless that kind of compact is entered into,"},{"time":1100000,"text":"you will not be able to sustain the consensus."}]}]}